0010 REM "ARC - Customer SpeedSearch (Comments)"
0020 REM "Program ARC.QC"
0022 REM "+-----------------------------------------------------------+"
0024 REM "| ADD+ON Software, Inc. Advantage/V Version 6.0.0 - 15May96 |"
